title: myNetwork
description: myNetwork is a web application written with a React-Redux frontend and a Rails API backend. It gives users full CRUD capabilities over their contacts and reminders for those contacts.

title: myTowne
description: myTowne is a community bulletin board written with a React-JS frontend and a Rails API backend. It gives users full CRUD capabilities for their own posts and profile and read capabilities for community member's posts.

title: Animagus
description: Animagus is a web application written in Vanilla JavaScript that shows simple DOM manipulation in a fun interactive game.
